messages.message:
I have a PR that is giving me this TravisCI message:
```Travis CI - Pull Request Expected — Waiting for status to be reported```
and it doesnt seem to want to end. Anyone seen this before?

Happened to me 2 days ago, I guess something wrong happened when travis got notified about the new PR, the PR is waiting on Travis’s status but at the same time Travis doesn’t have build in place for that PR
I pushed a dummy commit so I can nudge Travis to start a build process for my PR
```git commit --allow-empty```
